## [Master] - 2026/05/29

### Changed

- MAJOR The CHANGELOG structure of Lethe has been completely changed. The previous implementation relied on a single .md file that would contain the contents of everyone. Regrettably, this led to multiple file conflicts and a large number of rebase that were not necessary. This PR fixes this by introducing a new CHANGELOG structure where every change is now stored in /release_notes/current/. The release_notes/template.md file contains the instruction regarding the content of the individual changelog files [#2006](https://github.com/chaos-polymtl/lethe/pull/2006).